description: Zinzino AB engages in the direct selling business. The company is headquartered in Vaestra Froelunda, Vastra Gotalands and currently employs 102 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2010-09-20. The company offers dietary supplements which regulate the ratio of omega-6 and omega-3 acids in the body. Its offering is available under the brand Balance and includes supplements in a form of shakes, oils and capsules.
name: Zinzino AB
